title: Image Processing App
description: Image classifier using a K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN) algorithm to predict the time of day an image was taken.

title: Power Outage Analysis
description: Performed exploratory data analysis of a nationwide power outage dataset using Pandas and data visualization techniques, revealing key factors impacting outage durations. Built a Random Forest Regression model with Scikit-Learn to predict the duration of power outages based on causes and population statistics of affected areas.

title: Yelp Ratings Predictor
description: Performed feature engineering and developed machine learning model using PyTorch to predict Yelp review ratings (star count) based solely on the review text.

title: Weather and Tourism in San Diego
description: Data visualization project that anaylzes the way sunshine and rain affect tourism rates in San Diego.
